sub_title: Creative open for freelance or permanent opportunities in Amsterdam and beyond.
summary: Visually exploring how to make a mark on the world, learn from multicultural experiences, and connect with people, all over a cup of coffee. I believe in conversation, mutual understanding, hard work, dedication, creative expression, and the power of art and design. On the day to day I'm working for brands and agencies to help make work that counts in advertising, communications, and branding. On the side I'm currently creative directing my own magazine that showcases art from the Middle East and North Africa to Europe and the US in order to bridge the cultural gap and start transformative conversations. See my work and a first glance of my magazine at: amiartiz.com
